You can then enable invoices, so that invoices are automatically created in QuickBooks from accepted Quotient quotes. name: ScaleXP
tag_line: Most comprehensive B2B reporting system
details:
ScaleXP is the most comprehensive reporting system for B2B or SAAS companies:
- Automate deferred revenue recognition.  Continue invoicing your customers in QuickBooks. Invoices are pulled into ScaleXP will have revenue schedules calculated automatically.
- Understand and track net revenue and net customer growth, including new, lost, upgrades and downgrades
- Automate unit economics, customer lifetime value, cost of customer acquisition, even cohort analysis 
- Consolidate multiple countries or accounting systems
- Actionable insights plus a series of reports and dashboards tailored to your business.  
It's so simple, yet profound...try it.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
ScaleXP seamlessly integrates with QuickBooks Online and your CRM platform to transform your accounting data into a full suite of metrics and KPIs.  The dashboards and visual performance reports provide actionable insights which arm you with the data to understand each part of the organisation - from sales to marketing to operations.  
ScaleXP uses sophisticated algorithms to seamlessly join invoices and manual journals to CRM data, providing an instant and granular view of your customer data.  Financial consolidation modules and multi-currency functionality are included as standard.
key_benefits:
Create a single source of truth:  ScaleXP links QuickBooks and your CRM system, providing a superbly granular view of your data.  Trends are visualised in graphs with click through functionality to nominal code detail, creating a single truth.
Be prepared for your next funding round.  The system automatically tracks all SAAS and B2B KPIs and metrics:  MRR, ARR, LTV, CAC, even cohort analysis.  The system automatically suggests metrics; additional KPIs can be turned on and off in a click.
Save time and get more done.   Detailed cost tracking allows you to monitor the performance of each department, using QuickBook Classes or multi-report views.  Multiple companies and currencies are easily consolidated.   Share data in just one click.

name: PerpetualInvoice
tag_line: Super batch invoicing computes custom item usage by customer. Fast and powerful.
details: PI.com's mission is to create large numbers of invoices in QuickBooks Online, quickly and automatically.  This saves you labor, gets invoices out fast for improved cash flow and reduces customer service through better quality. Jobs are created and managed using customer and item lists. The designator customer list invoices against the current customer and maintains a billing history by customer by designator. Designators are the units of revenue producing entities; service addresses, lot numbers, apartment numbers, etc. Items in QuickBooks Online can be extended in PI.com to include min/max qtys and amounts, variable rates, classes...more!
how_it_works_with_quick_books: PI.com provides a comprehensive interface to QuickBooks Online including: customers, items, invoices and companies. Accounts on PI.com have the ability to create and edit the above mentioned objects in QuickBooks Online. The login/access capability is ideal for Pro Advisors and Users that have access to multiple QuickBooks  Online companies. Collaborate internally by adding your staff to the account. Creation and edits to objects in QuickBooks Online are real-time and bi-directional. Batch jobs in PI.com run completely remotely from QuickBooks Online.
key_benefits:
Unique batch invoicing that supports any business and is list driven gets your billing out to your customers faster without errors saving you time and money. Computes custom item usage by customer.  ProAdvisor  friendly, multi-company, multi-user.
PerpetualInvoice lets you describe the resource (designator) that generates revenue for you and assigns customers to each resource providing a manageable list for accurate billing and a history of the customers and revenue generated. Accountant ready
PI.com provides an Item engine that models nearly any price. Extending the Item calculations to provide min/max quantities, variable rates, classes plus Rules gives you the ultimate in item pricing. Utilizes Excel for custom calculations, readings.

name: Gozynta Mobius
tag_line: Connect your financial data to ConnectWise Manage in minutes!
details: What Gozynta Mobius does is as easy as A, Bee, C. It connects ConnectWise Manage to QuickBooks Online. When invoices are created in Manage, Gozynta Mobius can copy them to QuickBooks Online. When payments are created against those invoices in QuickBooks Online, it copies those payments to Manage. In addition, it copies expenses and inventory information from Manage to QuickBooks Online. You need to be a busy bee to get all that data inputted and up to date. Gozynta Mobius does it in a click.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Gozynta Mobius is a web-app that allows partners to connect between QuickBooks Online and ConnectWise Manage.
Choose the type of transaction you want to send over (Invoices, Expenses, Inventory, or ALL), and click Submit. Done.
All of our plans feature automatic payment sync. You receive your payments in QuickBooks, and we'll enter them into Manage for you.
We play nice with payment platforms
Want to use QuickBooks built-in payment engine? Send your invoices from QuickBooks and your customers can click on the link to pay online. We have a process that makes it easy.
key_benefits:
Auto-creation? The integration will automatically create new customers, vendors, and products in QuickBooks Online for any records that do not already exist.
Single record batches ? Individually select which transactions you want to batch over.
Automatic Syncing:
Is 2 clicks too many? We'll give you zero-click. Upgrade to our Standard plan, turn on auto-sync, and we'll batch over your transactions automatically in the background while you do other things.
Unlimited is our favorite word
Rather than nickel and diming you to death, all of our paid plans allow for unlimited transactions.
Unlimited Invoices
Unlimited Expenses
Unlimited Payments
Even Unlimited QuickBooks Companies
pricing_text: We charge our customers on a monthly plan and there are no term limits. We even have a free tier. Our annual pricing saves you money, as well!

name: Transaction Pro
tag_line: Easily and effortlessly get data into and out of QuickBooks Online
details:
Since 2005, Transaction Pro has been the trusted name in data import, export and delete tools with QuickBooks. Transaction Pro makes it fast and easy to move transactions and lists into and out of QuickBooks via Excel or CSV files. A simple one-time mapping is all it takes; no complicated templates. 

Transaction Pro can save you hours of time and relieve the burden of manually entering transactions into QuickBooks. Plus you know your data is error-free since we validate your file to be sure everything is correct. 

Simply drag and drop your file, map the fields and start moving data in minutes!
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Transaction Pro for QuickBooks Online includes the new Admin Portal, allowing you to add multiple companies and users under one subscription. Once added, you can easily import, export and delete data including transactions and lists using Excel or CSV files. A simple and powerful way to exchange data with QuickBooks Desktop or Online.
key_benefits:
EASY. Transaction Pro was designed for ease of use. We understand you want to get your job done quickly and without a long learning curve. Our products are designed by business people, for business people.
FAST. Transaction Pro utilizes the latest Intuit APIs to ensure the fastest possible uploads. We work hard to be sure you are getting the maximum performance when using our tools. We are constantly adding new features and more value to our products.
TRUSTED. Since 2005, Transaction Pro has been the trusted name for data imports and exports for QuickBooks. We were the first and remain the most trusted data importer for QuickBooks. Why risk your critical accounting data to imitators?
pricing_text: Free trial available. Plans start as low as $10/mo. More plans available, visit our website at https://www.transactionpro.com or email us at sales@transactionpro.com.

name: Practice Ignition

details:
Practice Ignition is a digital proposal and payment processing platform. It allows you to easily onboard new and existing clients, combining three key parts of your process into one smooth transaction. Proposal. A signed engagement letter. And payment for your services. All in one Platform.

Practice Ignition also integrates with Intuit Practice Management powered by Karbon to bring the same benefits to your tax workflow.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Practice Ignition automatically creates invoices inside QuickBooks Online based on the payment schedule listed in your proposal. 

It automatically will raise and reconcile the invoice, as well as send that invoice to the client automatically, every single month.

If you have monthly billing cycles with your clients or you do alot of project work. Practice Ignition can help simplify the entire process. From putting your best foot forward with our marketing brochures to then automating all the admin required to get paid and keep your QuickBooks account up to date.
key_benefits: Practice Ignition will help you provide on an online digital check-out process for your clients to digitally sign and engage you for the work you're about to do for them. We've helped firms eliminate 100% of their debtors through our platform.

name: Decision Maker
tag_line: Turn your QuickBooks data into profitable financial decisions
details:
The Decision Maker provides the best decisions to reach maximum profitability. 


This easy-to-use software comes ready with 18 innovative modules organized in 3 sections: 
VIEW ? DECIDE ? ADVISOR 


VIEW SECTION - Financial reports provided: 
Dashboard, Financial statements, Products / Services report, Costs report,
Break-even, ratios, Business valuation, Financial grade. 


DECIDE SECTION - Simulations you can do: 
Spending, Profit, Payback, Break-Even, Profit & Loss, Budget


AI ADVISOR SECTION ? Provides you with: 
Short-term suggestions, Long-term suggestions
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Connecting your QuickBooks to the Decision Maker is very simple and just takes seconds.  
Under Settings ? Click - Add a company 
1.     Fill-out you company details
2.	You have the option to add your logo
3.	Under Preferences - in Accounting System - Choose US GAAP
4.     Under Data Input ? Click on the QuickBooks logo, then Next, and Connect to QuickBooks
5.	Sign-in to your QuickBooks account  to accept the connection to the Decision-Maker. 
That?s it. You are now ready to experience the powerful and innovative tools the Decision Maker offers
key_benefits:
Easily access your analytics to know exactly where you stand financially at any given time
Simulate effortlessly your data to determine the future impact of any financial decision you want to make today
Comes ready with a smart AI advisor that analyzes your company non-stop and is always seeking to increase your overall profitability and business value.

name: G-Accon
tag_line: Google Sheets Add-On for QuickBooks. Automate reporting and data entry.
details:
G-Accon lets you connect & sync Google Sheets with QuickBooks bidirectionally.
Share sheets & collaborate with your team & clients in real-time.
Refresh your spreadsheets automatically using a flexible schedule. Create BI dashboards by connecting your spreadsheets to Google Data Studio and setting auto-refresh.
Save a lot of time by automating your reporting and data entry tasks.
Automatically save snapshots in Google Drive to keep historical data.
Send real-time reports to your clients automatically in Excel, PDF, CSV. 
We offer to our clients the efficient, reusable & time effective solution.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: G-Accon for QuickBooks has the ability to connect Google Sheets to multiple QuickBooks entities and consolidate data. 2-way sync will allow you to edit data and bulk upload to multiple QuickBooks companies directly from Google Sheets. Use templates to customize and automate data exports, reports, and uploads. Save your templates in Cloud and share with anyone. Our product also offers the ability to automate data refresh using a flexible schedule (hourly, daily, monthly, weekly), schedule backups (snapshots) of historical data, set up data monitoring & alerts, and send emails.
key_benefits:
Easily connect Google Sheets with multiple QuickBooks companies in 2-way sync. Save a lot of time by scheduling automatic exports, data refreshes, bulk uploads to QuickBooks directly from Google Sheets.
Use the power of Google Sheets + G-Accon custom templates to build and automate reports & dashboards. Save, reuse, and share your templates in Cloud.
Automatically email real-time reports to your clients. Easily share, comment, and collaborate in Google Drive. Work as a team on a shared spreadsheet, enter data and it will be automatically synced with QuickBooks Online.

name: eClientLink Custom Report Generator
tag_line: Financial Statement Report Writer and Chart Editor for Online and Desk Top
details:
Non-Profits can produce reports which are not available in QuickBooks. Statement of Activity reports (Profit and Loss) can be prepared that report unrestricted funds and restricted funds. Plus numerous other Non-Profit reports.

Consolidated financial statements can be prepared from several QuickBooks companies. Consolidating eliminating entries and currency conversion entries can be made.

Almost any statement you can imagine can be created. If the data is in QuickBooks, or can be calculated from the data in QuickBooks, then it can be use on any statement.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Using the eClientLink Statement Wizard setup, the financial information is downloaded from QuickBooks, and formatted in the requested statement form. This statement can then be used as is, or additional customization can be done. Updating data from QuickBooks for a new period is done with a simple one button click. 

For more information  click here to visit our web site.

To keep informed about our App,  click here to add you name to our e-mail list.
key_benefits:
Financial Statement and Chart editor that creates customized Financial Statements and Charts from QuickBooks data. More customization available, than  in  QuickBooks. More Info
No need to export the QuickBooks reports to Excel and then sort, cut and paste, in order to get the report you need. Reports can be exported to Excel, ready to print or deliver, or they can be printed directly from the App.
The original version of this App was developed for a CPA firm to provide its clients with financial information. Myron Joy, the principal developer, has had more than 20 year's experience as a practicing CPA and a Certified QuickBooks Pro Adviser.
pricing_text:
Subscriptions start at $15.00 per Firm and are billed annually.

name: A2X
tag_line: Accurate ecommerce accounting for Shopify, Amazon, Etsy, Walmart & eBay sellers
details:
A2X automatically fetches & processes Shopify, Amazon, Etsy, Walmart & eBay settlements & payouts. Then generates journals for each settlement (independently for each sales channel) and posts them to QuickBooks Online, automatically.

Each time one of your sales channels initiates a settlement, A2X detects it, loads the transactions, & generates a summary of the revenue, expenses & various other transactions from that sales channel.

Configure A2X to aggregate sales by SKU, by product type, or by country. You select which ledger accounts and tax rates A2X should use for each transaction type.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
A2X makes it easy for you to account accurately for your ecommerce sales. A major time drain on any ecommerce accounting firm that has ecommerce seller clients is reconciling payouts from Shopify, Amazon, Etsy, Walmart and eBay.

A2X solves this problem by automatically sorting and aggregating your sales revenue, fees and other transaction data and slotting it into QuickBooks Online. You end up with accurate, reconciled financial records every month, without wasting your time. A2X supports sales through multiple marketplaces worldwide, and has multi-currency capability built-in.
key_benefits:
Have confidence in your ecommerce financials, knowing your numbers add up. 
A2X posts your Shopify, Amazon, Walmart, eBay and Etsy sales and fees directly into QuickBooks in tidy summaries that match the payments to your bank account.
Save hours every month.
The time-consuming task of importing transactions and using spreadsheets to do your accounting is a thing of the past with A2X. Our customers say it's saved them up to 20 hours of manual slog every month.
Set and forget.
A2X scales as your business does, no matter whether you're a small business or a large merchant with complex needs, A2X will support you as your business grows.
pricing_text: A2X plans start from $19/month. Plans scale up depending on order volume and ecommerce sales channel. Plans cater for larger sellers, and for those selling internationally with multi-currency.

name: Relay Financial
tag_line: Banking designed for growing businesses and their ProAdvisors.
details: Relay is banking designed for growing businesses and their ProAdvisors. Once you sign up, you?ll have access to as many FDIC-insured (up to $250,000 per business) business checking accounts as you need with powerful financial features to help your business thrive.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Relay shares a direct bank feed with QuickBooks Online and auto-syncs your banking data to make paying bills and reconciling accounts fast, easy, and reliable.

Unpaid bills in QuickBooks Online are auto-imported to Relay where you can set-up approval workflows and pay vendors via ACH, wire, or check.

Enriched transaction data (including category, check payee, and more) is auto-synced with QuickBooks Online in real-time for one-click reconciliation.
key_benefits:
Finally, a bank that makes your accounting easier, not harder. With Relay, you get all the features you would expect from your bank and so much more, including a powerful integration with QuickBooks Online.
Business owners can open as many checking accounts as they need without the monthly fees or minimum balances, issue Mastercard debit cards with spending limits, pay bills via ACH, wire, and check, and invite ProAdvisors to collaborate.
Relay shares a direct bank feed with QuickBooks Online to automatically import unpaid bills and send enriched transaction data (including category, check payee, and more) to the bank feed for fast, reliable reconciliation.
pricing_text:
Relay offers business banking with no account fees or minimum balances. Businesses get free checking accounts, Mastercard debit cards, ACH, and checks.

Charges apply for outgoing wires and Relay's advanced bill pay functionality.

Better stock control - Keep track of stock across multiple warehouses, in multiple locations, anywhere in the world. Unleashed lets you know exactly what stock you have, and where so you can make better business decisions.

name: WOWinflow
tag_line: Predictive Credit Control. Critical insights for your Credit Control.
details:
Critical Credit Control insights made easy with WOWinflow and QuickBooks Online.

WOWinflow - the payment predicting, bad-debt alerting, collection prioritising, 'click & go' add-on app for amazing Credit Control.

WOWinflow learns and monitors your customers REAL payment patterns - predicting all invoice payment dates, late payments, provides warnings about customers with potential cash problems and calculates accurate accounts receivable data by day, month or year for reliable forecasting.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: WOWinflow is easy to use - everything's automated. No training. No configuration. Seamlessly integrate with QuickBooks Online and set up in just a few clicks.

Get the earliest warnings possible to reduce risk and avoid bad debt.
Chase payment intelligently.

Cut your Accounts Receivable collection time by up to 75%.
Eliminate guesswork.

Know the dates that customers will pay your invoices and see exactly when cash will arrive in your business.

name: LOCATE Inventory
tag_line: Enterprise-level inventory & order management built for the mid-market.
details: LOCATE is a scalable, cloud-based inventory management solution designed to help product-based businesses succeed in the QuickBooks ecosystem. LOCATE's ERP-level features and dynamic workflows bring efficiency and productivity to growing companies, while summarized accounting keeps QuickBooks running lean and clean.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Inventory Designed with Accounting in Mind!  LOCATE continuously summarizes your company's transactions and syncs only essential information with QuickBooks. This keeps your QuickBooks data lean and clean, while LOCATE's internal inventory ledger and comprehensive audit trails provide full financial visibility.
key_benefits:
ERP-Level Inventory - From warehouse basics, such as kitting, barcoding & tracking (serial, lot, expiration, etc.), to advanced workflows like drop shipping, manufacturing & wave picking, LOCATE brings the power of an ERP system to QuickBooks.
Built to Scale - LOCATE is the ideal solution for inventory-based companies looking to harness the power of the cloud without any of the data caps, volume constraints, or financial "file bloat" found with traditional inventory software.
Mid-Market Solutions -  LOCATE supports the unique and dynamic needs of growing businesses with features like outsource manufacturing, 3PL workflows, inventory reservations, and use orders to manage samples and trade shows.

name: ApprovalMax
tag_line: Approvals & accounts payable automation for invoices, bills and purchase orders
details: Bill creation, review and approval
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
ApprovalMax powers up QuickBooks Online with multi-step multi-role approvals for accounts payable. Purchase orders and bills are created outside of QuickBooks Online and only enter the system after full authorization. Approval requests are routed based on QuickBooks Online data: vendor, amount, category, class, etc. A detailed audit trail is automatically generated and attached to each authorized document before it gets pushed to QuickBooks Online ready for payment.

Direct integration with Dext Prepare ensures a completely paperless process from data capture to bill approval.
key_benefits:
No more unauthorised expenses or late payments: ApprovalMax enables multi-step, multi-role authorisation for key accounts payable documents.
Pre-built integration with Dext Prepare: digitise your paper documents and then properly authorise them using an ApprovalMax approval workflow.
Make approvers? lives easier: business approvers, budget holders, executives can review and approve (or reject) purchase orders and bills via our mobile or web app; or by replying to the automated customisable notification they received.
pricing_text: ApprovalMax offers Standard and Premium plans with monthly or annual billing. A free 30-day trial for the Premium plan is available directly via the QuickBooks Online marketplace, and on https://www.approvalmax.com/quickbooks

name: PayPal by Sush.io
tag_line: PayPal Express Checkout sync on Autopilot by Sush.io
details:
Synchronize all your Paypal Charges, Purchases, Fees and Refunds in QuickBooks!

The charges are created as Sales Receipts in QuickBooks and the refunds as Refund Receipts. The Purchases are created as Expenses in QuickBooks. Fees are created either as Purchase items or Vendor Credit in case of a Refund.

Managing funds withdrawn

Users can initiate transfers from PayPal to their own Bank account but also to a Third Party account. Sush.io will create a Transfer if the money is sent to the user account and a purchase otherwise.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: As Sush.io is perfectly integrated with QuickBooks, you?ll spend less time to reconcile your Paypal account in QuickBooks. The match is automatically done, you simply have to approve transactions with a single click!
key_benefits:
Put your accounting on autopilot in just a few clicks now. Sush.io will sync Paypal Express Checkout and manage Money in (sales receipts, refunds), Money sent (purchase), Paypal fees and Funds.
Paypal Clearing account matches automatically all your Paypal Express Checkout transactions.
As Sush.io is perfectly integrated with QuickBooks, you?ll spend less time to reconcile your Paypal account in QuickBooks. The match is automatically done, you simply have to approve transactions with a single click!

name: Knowify for Contractors
tag_line: Job costing, progress invoicing, change orders, and more for construction firms.
details:
The construction industry is demanding higher efficiency and professionalism from all of its players. You cannot let your business fall behind. Knowify will help you step up.


Trusted in the US, Canada, UK and Australia, Knowify is the ideal solution for forward-thinking remodelers, residential contractors, and commercial subs that want to get an edge in the market by running a more efficient and professional business.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Sign up in seconds: Just click ?Get App Now? and Knowify will automatically import all the relevant data from QuickBooks.


No more double entry of invoices, bills or payments. Knowify keeps jobs, clients, vendors and items in sync bi-directionally, and syncs all invoices, time, payments and expenses for you seamlessly. You can even import all your expenses from QuickBooks for job costing purposes!


Keep the accounting and operational parts of the business in sync and focus on getting more jobs and helping your customers.
key_benefits:
Real-time job costing for materials, labor, subcontractors, and equipment. See where you stand across all your jobs, then zoom in on any given one to see real-time performance by phase of work.
Flexible and robust invoicing methods, including progress invoicing, pay apps for commercial work, schedule of values, and more. Whether you bill fixed price or time and materials, Knowify can help you save hours in your invoicing process.
All the other tools you need to run your contracting business, including contract and change order management (with built-in e-signature capture), scheduling, time tracking, mobile access from the field, team notifications and alerts, and more!
pricing_text: 14 Day Free Trial.  No Credit Card Required.

name: exportmybooks.com
tag_line: QuickBooks Online to QuickBooks Desktop conversion made easy
details: Ready to make the switch? Securely connect to your QuickBooks Online company and we'll convert your data into a QuickBooks Desktop company file that's ready to go, so you can be up and running in no time.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Moving from QuickBooks Online to QuickBooks Desktop has never been easier. 
exportmybooks.com connects directly to your QuickBooks Online company, converts the information, and creates a new version as a QuickBooks Desktop company file, keeping all your data intact. Simply download your new file, open it in QuickBooks Desktop, and pick up right where you left off.
key_benefits:
Easy. exportmybooks.com allows you to skip the complicated data export and import process and provides you with a .qbb backup company file with just a couple clicks. Makes moving from QuickBooks Online to QuickBooks Desktop a breeze.
Fast. exportmybooks.com saves you valuable time by quickly converting your QuickBooks Online data for you so you can get your company up and running on QuickBooks Desktop within 24 hours.
Secure. We connect directly to your QuickBooks Online company with bank-level 128-bit SSL encryption so your sensitive company and customer information is always safe.

details:

2. Send an IVR message when a new invoice over $1000 is created in QuickBooks

name: Ramp
tag_line: Ramp is the only card that helps you and your company spend less.
details:
On the Accounting page, click on 'QuickBooks' in the Connect an Accounting Integration section. Enter your QuickBooks credentials and then click Sign-In. At the prompt, click Connect and you will be redirected back to Ramp.
Select an accounts payable account in QuickBooks to sync with, and then configure your category mappings. You can then review and sync your transactions!
how_it_works_with_quick_books: The Ramp QuickBooks App allows you to seamlessly push your Ramp Card transaction data to QuickBooks, and helps ensure that every transaction ends up in the right expense account.  You'll be able to specify one of your expense accounts for each Ramp Category, and you'll be able to review each transaction before it leaves Ramp, making changes if needed.  You can push all of your transactions at the end of the month, or you can review them in smaller batches.  After you've completed your review, Ramp will push your transactions to QuickBooks, where they will appear as QuickBooks Expenses.
key_benefits:
Unlike other cards that want you to spend more, Ramp is the only card that helps you keep your money in your bank account. On top of our automated saving features, we guarantee 1.5% money back on all spending. No exceptions, no points, just cash.
With one-click receipt reminders you can quickly notify everyone who owes you a receipt. No more hunting people down.
We automatically match all your receipts to the correct transaction and automate away the infamous expense report. Simply text or forward a receipt and we'll do the rest.
pricing_text: The Ramp QuickBooks Integration is completely free to use.

name: Atto - Employee Time & Location Tracking
tag_line: The simplest time clock app for SMEs, generating timesheets ready for payroll.
details:
Atto is the simplest timesheet app for small businesses. Tap a button to clock in and start tracking your time. Your work hours turn into simple, accurate timesheet reports automatically.

Detailed insights into your team's daily activity give you actionable knowledge that helps you grow your business. Find out instantly who?s on the clock, on break, hasn?t showed up for work yet or is enjoying some time off. Generate powerful timesheet reports automatically, including regular time, overtime, breaks, jobs and pto.

Increase accountability and never second-guess your team?s timesheet reports again. Save time and money and focus on real growth.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Our seamless integration with QuickBooks Online helps you easily track your team?s time
and manage your business with accurate and reliable data. 

Your employee timesheets are calculated automatically and synced to QuickBooks Online on the spot, avoiding errors and second-guessing. During our simple integration process, you match your employees' accounts from QuickBooks Online to Atto and their timesheets are synced from Atto to QuickBooks Online in real time. You can add or remove employees with a simple click of a button at any time.
key_benefits:
SIMPLE TIME TRACKING
Whether in the office or while on the move, time tracking has never been simpler. Just tap a button to clock in and start tracking your time.

While on the clock, track time towards specific job codes, add notes or take a break.
GPS LOCATION TRACKING
Get real-time updates on your team?s location. Mobile GPS tracking helps you ensure everyone is safe, productive and in the right place at the right time.

Location tracking turns off as soon as you clock out.
AUTOMATED TIMESHEETS
Empower your team with automated timesheets and get accurate reports, including regular time, overtime and PTO. Never second-guess your timesheet report?s accuracy again.

You run your business. We?ll take care of your timesheets

name: Checkbook
tag_line: Send Digital Checks instead of Paper Checks.
details:
Receiving Digital ChecksFirst time recipients will be asked to verify their identity online. This process takes 60 seconds for 'instant verification' using online banking credentials, or 24 hours for 'manual verification' using micro-deposits to the recipient's bank account. After this first time, all future Digital Checks are automatically deposited.
Recipients don't need to signup to receive payment.They can also print Checks at home or ask for a mailed paper Check.
We want to support all your Vendor's preferences. So, our additional deposit options are flexible!
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Installing the Checkbook App  
Click on ?Get App Now? to authorize Quickbooks to integrate with Checkbook. You will be redirected to checkbook.io to verify your bank account instantly. After bank verification, your checks will be recognized and sent as Digital Checks.  
Sending Checks from Quickbooks 
You can create a Check transaction directly from Quickbooks & mark it as "Print Later" to alert our system to pick it up and send a Digital Check. Use the "Pay Bills" screen instead with the same method to send many Checks at once.
key_benefits:
Digital Checks are delivered over email  
Digital Checks are a digital replacement for cumbersome and costly paper checks. All your Digital Checks are delivered to Vendors using their registered vendor email.
Digital Checks can be deposited into any bank account in the US  
Digital Checks are instantly and automatically deposited into any bank account that your vendor chooses to. We support all banks in the United States.
We also mail traditional paper Checks to your Vendors for you  
If your Vendor does not want to deposit their Digital Check online, they can simply print it out themselves, or ask for a paper Check mailed to them through USPS.
pricing_text: No sign-up fee. $9.95/month - send your first three Digital Checks for free!

details:
Veem is a global payments solution built for small businesses and the accountants & bookkeepers who support them. It?s the easiest way to send and receive payments internationally to and from over 110 countries at better rates than banks.

Veem lets you invite your bookkeeper, accountant, or your team while assigning varying levels of authority. You can easily pay and get paid with our secure and compliant payment process. name: Arka Inventory
tag_line: Advanced inventory  & production management built on Salesforce
details:
Arka brings multi-location inventory management and bill of material features to QuickBooks Online.

Benefits of using Arka:

1. Helps you understand your product costs better
2. Gives you visibility & control over your inventories
3. Saves you costs through inventory optimisation
4. Helps you make timely purchases
5. Helps you to take right pricing decisions
6. Brings your purchase, production, finance & sales teams together
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Purchase orders created in QuickBooks are automatically synced to Arka as expected items to receive in the warehouse. When such items are marked as received, inventories are created in the corresponding warehouse.

Bill of material feature will help to record conversion of raw materials in to finished goods and track accurate cost of products produced.

Invoices created in QuickBooks will sync as shipments from warehouse in Arka reducing the inventories and calculating the cost of goods sold.

Arka will give you accurate cost of each product and helps to tracks inventory in each location.
key_benefits:
Helps to track inventory in multiple locations to get better visibility & control over product inventories.
Helps to convert raw materials in to finished goods and track cost of goods produced and margins for each individual product SKUs.
Helps to allocate service costs like transportation, duties etc to inventories to get landed costs of products.

name: Joiin
tag_line: Manages group consolidations with ease - Consolidates Multi Currency and Entity
details:
Consolidated financial reporting made easy - automate the way you consolidate financial, sales and KPI data. Create eye-catching custom reports, quickly and seamlessly with your QuickBooks data and collaborate with your team easily across multiple devices from anywhere in the world. All at the touch of a button.

With a wealth of reporting power at your fingertips, quickly run key financial reports including balance sheet, trial balance, cashflow, and profit and loss reports, as well as fully featured custom reports and personalised reporting packs, all with multi currency capabilities as standard.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Seamlessly integrates with QuickBooks Online and other financial data sources to provide clear, consolidated reports.  A simple two-click process links your QuickBooks company to Joiin.  Joiin then takes care of importing your financial data automatically.  Import takes seconds and then you're ready to run reports across multiple companies.  Joiin automatically refreshes the data on a regular basis so your reports are always up to date.  Simple click to add and remove companies as required.
key_benefits:
Manage multi-entity and multi-currency group consolidations with ease. Both off the shelf reports  and custom reporting allows you to create bespoke consolidated reports, save them in management reporting packs and deliver them with a touch of a key.
Multi-Client and Multi-User functionality helps finance teams, advisors and their clients collaborate seamlessly across all devices. Providing team members and clients their own unique login to view consolidated data on the move.
With our dedicated support team on hand to solve any issues and ensure an easy transition, you'll be up to speed in no time. Our comprehensive support package includes on-boarding, one-to-one technical support and a dedicated help centre.

details:

Financial analytics at your fingertips. Construct and refine balance sheets and P&Ls. Insert total rows, modify groupings, add formulas in powerful spreadsheets, and all with live data.

Budgets and forecasts built off of advanced formulas...and always live. Consolidate multiple businesses easily.

Take back your time by creating sticky reports, that stay updated, and refresh the data regularly. Even the text can be live. Now you can build a report once then refine and perfect it over time, rather than rebuilding it and all of its source data every month.

Master your reporting.

Astound your clients with master reports.

Enhance financial spreadsheets with quickly digestible visual metrics, reports, and dashboards in minutes. Your clients will be amazed at how easy it is to understand the reports you provide.

name: nettTracker
tag_line: Fixed Assets Made Easy...Very Easy
details:
What does nettTracker do for you?

1. Detects new Capital purchases by monitoring QuickBooks transactions in accounts you specify

2. Creates new Fixed Asset entries, specifies depreciation rules and projects depreciation costs

3. Calculates depreciation and creates the journal entries in QuickBooks Online

4. All of the above can be set to processed automatically, keeping your balance sheet up to date in real-time
how_it_works_with_quick_books: When creating the nettTracker company file and connecting to QuickBooks Online, the user chooses which chart of account codes need to be monitored for fixed asset purchases.  The user also sets up asset groups which will determine where fixed assets are added to, how depreciation is calculated, and which accounts in QuickBooks will be effected by the depreciation journals that are created by nettTracker.  The user can review the fixed asset summary in nettTracker which should agree to the balance sheet in QuickBooks Online.
key_benefits:
Saves time: nettTracker can automatically add capital purchases to your fixed asset register,  calculate depreciation and then post journals to QuickBooks Online
Saves money:  Over the year, many hours can be spent updating fixed asset registers, especially if they need to be maintained on a monthly basis.  Leave it to nettTracker and simply review the fixed asset register when you need to.
Increased accuracy:  Without the need to create spreadsheets and create and copy formulas, you can be sure that your depreciation is being calculated accurately with minimum effort.
pricing_text: Prices shown are Great British Pounds excluding VAT, payable each month.  Accounting firms connecting multiple clients can benefit with our tiered pricing structure.  All details can be found on our website www.nett-tracker.com/pricing

Where more than 10 companies are required, the price per company reduces further.  Please contact support for more information.', 'users': 'Unlimited', 'price': '2.50 GBP per month'}]

FAQs:
[{'question': 'Is it possible to import my existing fixed asset register into nettTracker?', 'answer': 'Yes.  We provide an Excel template that you can download and use to import your existing assets.  It is a quick and simple process.'}, {'question': 'What if an asset is added in error?', 'answer': 'Assets created based on a QuickBooks Online transaction that was misposted are flagged by nettTracker once the misposting has been detected.  These assets can be simply deleted.  

Deletion reverses ALL journal entries that may have been created for the asset.

We allow assets to be deleted only when in their first financial year, after which the asset will need to be disposed.  Any imported assets (ie from previous financial years) can only be disposed.'}, {'question': 'Is full automation mandatory?', 'answer': "No.  We provide granular control over the automation processes.  

You can choose whether to allow nettTracker to automatically process your monthly depreciation journals, rescan your transaction data and whether asset entries should be created automatically from new transactions.  These settings are all available within the 'Company' settings within the nettTracker app."}, {'question': 'Can I export the nettTracker fixed asset register?', 'answer': 'Yes.  You are able to export the asset register as an Excel file at any time.'}]

Zigaflows allows you to manage your opportunity pipeline, quotations, orders, jobs, projects, invoices, delivery notes, purchase orders, eForms, contracts, and tickets in one integrated system so nothing goes missing.

Use the quick link to jump from an invoice in Zigaflow to the invoice in QuickBooks.
key_benefits:
Compete better with a quicker turnaround of impressive documents - create attractive and professional quotes quickly and include images and custom information.
Allow Clients to approve with the integrated electronic signature.
Automate your office operations - Set up email sequences to chase your clients and staff to make sure nothing is forgotten. Automate the generation of jobs, invoices and other documents, as well as automatically pushing invoices into QuickBooks.
Reduce double typing and make your operations simpler by using one system to manage your quotes, orders/jobs, delivery notes, invoices, purchase orders, contracts, tickets, and eForms. Use the integrated CRM to manage your clients with their orders.
pricing_text:
There are three plans: Quotes Only, Automated Office, and Automation & Service. There is no minimum number of users for any of the plans.
Try out the full Zigaflow for 14-days for free with no credit card required.

name: Price Checkup

details:
Price Check generates a diagnostic report that can be used as the basis for a price conversation between accountants or bookkeepers and their clients. The financial insights in the report can help add value to a business.

Many businesses haven?t changed their prices in years, yet making even a small change can have a powerful effect. For many small businesses, a price change can mean the difference between staying open and closing its doors.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Price Check runs two years of QuickBooks invoices through its algorithms to generate an instant report that shows how a business?s prices have changed over time. This is done without storing any client financial data.
key_benefits:
Increase revenue without needing to make additional sales or hire more people.
Avoid disruptions in business and client attrition due to sudden forced price increases.
Identify the impact of discounting, frequent price changes, and selling products outside of core offerings.
pricing_text:
Although Price Check will eventually include more pricing plans, the app is currently free. 

During these uncertain times, we encourage people to try it out and see how it can help businesses survive and ultimately thrive.

name: Float
tag_line: Intuitive cash flow forecasting - see your future bank balance
details: Float provides a quick and easy solution to cash flow forecasting. Gone are the days of spending hours every month trying to bring your spreadsheet up to date only for it to go out of date the next time you process a transaction. As Float automatically reads all of your bills, invoices and actuals in QBO, it provides you with an always up to date, accurate cash flow forecast in a matter of minutes.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
How much cash will you have in the bank tomorrow? Next week? Next month? Float integrates seamlessly with QuickBooks to build a visual, easy-to-understand picture of your current and future cash. It's the only cash flow app for QuickBooks Online that updates your expectations with actuals every day. 

We import every bill and invoice from QuickBooks Online, enabling you to set accurate 'expected' payment dates that can be different from the official due date, making your forecast a true reflection of your cash position.

Faster and simpler than Excel. Plus it never goes out of date!
key_benefits:
Accurate data you can trust: Float provides an accurate, visual representation of your real cash position, giving you confidence in your current and future cash status.
Time saving: Save time on manual cash flow forecasting with automatic updates every 24 hours with what's really happening in your business, and trust that the information will always be accurate.

name: CashFlowXpert
tag_line: Enhanced AR mgmt tool-Get paid more quickly, reduce bad debts, improve cash flow
details:
AR management is time-consuming but it?s key to managing your cash flow and minimizing bad debts.  CashFlowXpert automatically gives you a new set of analytical and predictive tools you haven?t had before to make the job easier and faster. And it gives them to you in a flexible and easy to use environment.   

With a click of your mouse, you?ll be able to see how long a customer is taking to pay their invoices and the trend in their payment timeliness. Want to know how much CashFlowXpert predicts you?ll receive over the next week, 30 days, etc. based on customers? payment history?  It?s on the dashboard and immediately available.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Setup is quick and easy.  As soon as CashFlowXpert is connected with QuickBooks Online the app?s analytical and predictive tools are available and ready to use.  The app imports all of your customers and invoices with a balance due as well as invoices paid within the last 6 months. CashFlowXpert automatically syncs with QuickBooks daily and on-demand at any time. 

The only setup required is creating and customizing your payment reminder templates and enabling or disabling automated reminders on a company, customer and invoice level.   (Automated reminders are available in the Pro Edition)
key_benefits:
Get Paid Faster with Enhanced Payment Reminders - Customizable and personalized payment reminders offer more flexibility in the content and format of your reminders. Plus, you?re not restricted to a limited number of reminder templates.
Minimize bad debts with additional credit management tools - How long is it taking your customers to pay and what is the trend in their payment timeliness? It?s important information you need to manage your receivables and minimize your bad debts.
Better plan your cashflow - Knowing when you can expect to receive collections will help you plan your cashflow. CashFlowXpert?s intelligence predicts when your customers will pay based on their payment history over the last 6 months.

name: Order Time inventory
tag_line: Cloud Inventory and Order Management Platform
details:
Clock-like precision and control from anywhere with the cloud.  
From light Manufacturing to Wholesale to eCommerce, Order Time from NumberCruncher provides powerful control over orders, customers, and inventory in a single, easy system from any device, anywhere in the world, anytime, anywhere.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
QuickBooks is used for accounting while Order Time is used for operations.   Data that is used by both such as customers and vendors can be added or modified in either program.   

Transactions such as purchase orders and sales orders are maintained in Order Time.  Upon completion, the appropriate posting (e.g. Invoice or Bill) is recorded in QuickBooks. 

Synchronization can be scheduled or on demand.
key_benefits:
From purchasing and production to order entry, shipping and warehouse management, Order Time gives you control over orders, customers, and inventory in a single, easy-to-use system accessible from any device, anywhere in the world. anytime.

Purchasing and production automation tools ensure inventory levels keeps up with demand.   It takes the guesswork out of shipping.  know which order can ship in an instant.  With shipping integration pick, pack and ship operations run smoothly.

name: HireHop Equipment Rental Software
tag_line: HireHop - Equipment Rental Software
details:
HireHop introduces new important features never seen before in equipment rental software, from asset management features like simple pre-prep and stock checks, to new administration features like job calendars and full email integration.

No matter if you are a small or large company, HireHop can work for you. It possesses a plethora of functionality that will satisfy any larger company, and for the small to micro companies, a solution that has all the functionality they need and that they can grow into.

HireHop is intuitive and easy to use, yet it is incredibly powerful.  

Start using HireHop today for free and contact us for a free demo.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Create invoices, credit notes, purchase orders, contacts and register payments for invoices in HireHop that will seamlessly syncronize with QuickBooks in the background.

All payments logged against invoices created in HireHop will seamlessly be sent back to HireHop.

The sync can either be seamless and behind the scenes, or done in one batch at a time, whichever suits you.

You can even sync multiple organisations in QuickBooks with one installation of HireHop, as maybe each depot is a different organisation, or you have more than one organisation in a depot.
key_benefits:
HireHop is cloud based like QuickBooks, meaning there are no setup costs, no installation costs, no servers needed by you and it works on any computer, tablet or phone anywhere in the world.
Powerful and fully featured equipment rental software to manage your assets, invoices, availability, jobs and projects, with an easy to use and familiar interface.
HireHop is customizable and flexible, meaning HireHop works around you and your company's workflows, and not the other way round.

details:

name: Genie
tag_line: Granting Accounting Automation Wishes
details:
Genie layers on top of QuickBooks to provide a more fully-featured accounting and workflow system:  
-Manage accrual accounting such as Prepaid Expenses and Deferred Revenue.  Receive monthly journal entries for posting to QuickBooks as well as audit-ready accounting schedules.
-Create custom financial reporting packages in Genie to get better insight of your business.  Generate with the click of the mouse.
-Bring transparency to the status of monthly close activities including to dos and quality reviews.  Flag abnormal balances for resolution.
-Monitor transaction volumes and scope of service for clients to proactively manage engagements.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Genie syncs data from QuickBooks Online, and then applies automated rules and AI to flag and manage accounting, reporting, quality control, analytics, and client management processes.
key_benefits:
Automated Accrual Accounting:  Extend QuickBooks to be a true accrual-basis accounting system.  Manage accrual accounting needs such as Prepaid Expenses and Deferred Revenue in the system, not in manual spreadsheets.  Save time and improve accuracy!
Custom Reporting and Metrics:  Create more useful financial reports than are available in QuickBooks.  Include calculated rows and columns.  Pick and choose which data to display and what level of detail.  No more manual financial reporting in Excel!
Centralized Multi-Client Accounting and QC:  For firms and consultants, transparently manage monthly close to dos, status, and peer review.  Monitor transaction volumes and scope of service.  Proactively manage clients and stop being reactive!
pricing_text: Pricing is based on the number of modules and users.  Pricing begins at $50/mo per company and free trials are available.  Firms and consultants serving multiple clients can use a Firm subscription with multiple clients.

name: ConnectBooks
tag_line: Automated Bookkeeping/Accounting for Amazon Sellers
details:
ConnectBooks integrates with Amazon seller central to fetch all the data and import it into QuickBooks online. 

Each time amazon closes your settlement, ConnectBooks generates all the invoices, payments according to the settings you applied.

ConnectBooks offers robust reports and dashboards customized for e-commerce sellers.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Bookkeepers and Accountants proudly developed ConnetBooks.

There are many eCommerce integrations out there, but none succeed in capturing the complexities of Amazon.
As a Seller, your actual profit depends on so many factors, including shipping, storage, advertising, returns, inventory reimbursements, and all the other FBA fees.

At ConnectBooks, we wanted to create the Amazon sellers' most comprehensive system, capable of unifying an Amazon sellers' data and QuickBooks with 100% accuracy.

Finally, merchants everywhere can enjoy seamless automation explicitly built for the Amazon marketplace
key_benefits:
Stop wasting time with Excel spreadsheets. ConnectBooks will automate the process for you. We offer 15 different ways how to export your data to Quickbooks. No matter what size business you are, we have a solution for you.
Get your onboarding done by one of our experienced bookkeepers. 
We will walk you through step by step for seamless integration,
so your books are accurate to the penny.
ConnecBooks offers a live dashboard of your Amazon sales and FBA stock. In ConnectBooks, you will be able to see how much you earn per product, including a breakdown of all fees, order returns adjustment storage, and advertising.
pricing_text:
Pay when you have it.
At ConnectBooks we believe in our product, that's why we charge based on your success

name: CollBox
tag_line: A/R management and past-due invoice collections.
details:
Speed up your collection of unpaid invoices using CollBox to identify past-due accounts that need extra attention.

Your dedicated A/R professional will represent your company and be the human touch that is proven to collect faster than any automated messages.

Monitor status with the CollBox real-time dashboard to see which accounts need support and when you should expect payment.

CollBox will facilitate payment so you can keep focusing on running your business.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: CollBox connects directly with your QuickBooks account and pulls invoice records into a real-time dashboard that identifies which accounts are past-due and require additional attention.  Depending on the age of the unpaid invoice, CollBox provides 2 products (Assist & Collect) that help you collect and get paid fast.  Whether a customer has a recently past-due invoice and just needs a friendly reminder (Assist) or you have a seriously past-due invoice (90+ days) that requires Collections support (Collect), CollBox has you covered.
key_benefits:
Save time: Tracking down payments from customers is not the best use of your time, let CollBox follow up with your customers directly in a professional manner that works and gets you paid fast.
Accurate and reliable data: Real-time dashboard identifies which accounts are past-due recommends the best approach to collect on your unpaid invoice, whether it's sending to collections or just some A/R support.
Get paid faster: The ultimate goal is for you to get paid as fast as possible.  With our proven A/R techniques, you will collect your past-due invoices in record time.
pricing_text:
2 products for collecting unpaid invoices.
Collect - For 90+ day invoices. Zero risk, no upfront cost. We get paid from the Collection Agency fees.
Assist - Get a dedicated AR professional, starting at $250/mo. You keep 100% of the collected invoice.

Record sales, payouts, processing fees, track inventory on hand from different sources and auto-categorize transactions. Reconcile accounts in one click and enjoy your accurate monthly P&L and balance sheets!  More than 20 sales and payment platforms are supported.
The duplicate detector and 1-click rollback functionality secure your activity making sure your books are 100% accurate. Absolutely free trial with no credit card required!

Once connected to QuickBooks, Synder allows you to automatically synchronize activity from different platforms. The setup takes 5 minutes and requires 4 easy steps: 
Select platforms -> Connect -> Sync -> See results in QuickBooks
*You can switch between auto/manual sync mode at any time.

Connect all your sales channels to QuickBooks using just one Synder app and sync Stripe, Shopify, PayPal, Amazon, Square, eBay, Woo, BigCommerce, Etsy, Braintree, GoCardless, Afterpay, Cloverinstantly and with all the necessary details.
Import years of historical transactions into QuickBooks in just one click! Income and expenses will be auto-categorized with Synder's smart rules and your bank reconciliation will take literally 1 second!
Record sales, processing fees, payouts, refunds, expenses with all the details like items, customers, taxes, discounts, locations, shipping and even multi-currency - all you need to have for the perfect P&L, inventory and sales reports!

name: StarShip Shipping Software
tag_line: Small parcel & LTL shipping made simple!
details:
StarShip shipping software streamlines the shipping workflow by integrating directly to QuickBooks documents and providing advanced integration features:
1. Item - to automate international, LTL, HazMat and EDI functions
2. Inventory management - connect directly to Fishbowl or Acctivate to retrieve package > item detail
3. EDI - print GS1-128 labels with the carrier label then send details to your EDI provider to streamline ASN creation
4. Ecommerce - connect directly to your platform to read and write shipping detail OR update the ecommerce platform as an extension to QuickBooks.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Give your warehouse real-time access to QuickBooks orders, invoices or customer list to simplify the shipping workflow.  Order header and line details are translated and populated on the ship screen to eliminate duplicate entry and errors during shipping.   Once the shipment is processed, QuickBooks is updated immediately with freight charges and shipment detail.  Branded emails are also generated to reduce calls to customer service.
key_benefits:
QuickBooks Enterprise and QuickBooks Online plug-ins streamline shipping, accounts receivable and customer service in minutes with plug-and-play, bi-directional interfaces.  Additional connections to Fishbowl, Acctivate & EDI are also supported!
Access item detail to streamline documents and improve customer service
StarShip takes advantage of item-level detail to automate international (including ACE), hazardous and LTL shipments.  Item detail also enhances branded emails.
Ship small parcel and LTL from a single user interface
Rate shop to determine best method across modes.  StarShip supports over 2 dozen small parcel, LTL, 3PL and regional carriers including UPS, FedEx, USPS, WWEX, CH Robinson, YRC and more!
pricing_text: StarShip offers flexible pricing options to assist a wide range of companies.

name: Clockwurk
tag_line: Turn QuickBooks Online into a time clock
details: Make time tracking faster, easier, with less cost. Clockwurk has the features you need to track accurate hours for payroll. Clocking options such as wall-mounted time clocks, desktop computers, tablets, and phones. Features such as GPS tracking, IP punch security, automatic lunch deduction, punch rounding, shift schedules, weekly/daily overtime, and weekly/daily double time. Reporting such as timesheets, summaries, who's in reports, and punch exception reports. And equally important, fast, friendly customer service.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Clockwurk seamlessly integrates with QuickBooks Online. Simply connect your account, then import your workers. Simple as that. Workers can track time from anywhere and from any device. They can also track time from one of our cloud-based time clock terminals. But the real advantage of Clockwurk is what it does. It transfers worker start/stop times in real-time, enters those times on a QuickBooks timesheet, and separates any overtime or PTO hours on individual rows... just like an employee time clock system. Edit time in Clockwurk, everything else in QuickBooks!
key_benefits:
Seamless integration -- No need to map employees, contractors, classes, items, or jobs. It?s all handled automatically, and makes QuickBooks Online the source of truth.
Like a Time Clock -- Clockwurk enters the start/stop times for each worker. Much like a time clock. Know who is working, when they started, and when they left.
Real-time -- Every time a worker clocks in/out, or enters time, their hours are transferred to a QuickBooks timesheet instantly. No data exporting required.
pricing_text: Pay per worker plus a monthly base fee. We don't use expensive pricing tiers, and we don't overcharge per worker. Clockwurk is free for the first 15 days. No credit card required.

name: Stripe by Sush.io
tag_line: Your Stripe Accounting on Autopilot with Sush.io
details:
Synchronize all your Stripe Charges, Fees and Refunds.

The charges are created as Sales Receipts in QuickBooks and the refunds as Refund Receipts. The Fees are embedded in the deposit when a transfer occurs in Stripe.

Your Charges and Fees linked in the same Transfer.

For each Stripe transfer to your bank account, Sush.io automatically creates a deposit in QuickBooks with all matching Stripe Data (charges, fees and refunds).

Customize your setup.

Sush.io will allow you to choose sync date, account preferences, and more. Currency and other compatibility options are checked automatically to prevent any errors between Stripe and Quickbooks.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: As Sush.io is perfectly integrated with QuickBooks, you?ll spend less time to reconcile your Stripe transfers on your bank account in QuickBooks. The match is automatically done, you simply have to approve them!
key_benefits:
Put your Accounting on Autopilot in just a few clicks now. Sush.io will create Sales Receipts, Fees, Refunds, match Transfers to Deposits and more.
Automatically Match Stripe Transfers with Bank Transactions
Your Charges and Fees details within the same Transfer. Your Accounting always up-to-date.

details:

details:
Flex Catering is a web-based food & catering management software. It is all-in-one solution for corporate catering, restaurants, cafes and food businesses. Having the most advanced online ordering system for the food industry, Flex Catering is a comprehensive solution covering all aspects of running a catering business. It has advanced reports, integrations, dietary requirements and much more.

The app allows users to minimise data entry by sending their orders to QuickBooks with a click of a button. Customer details, products information and payment passes from Flex Catering to QuickBooks.

key_benefits:
Online Ordering for Food Businesses:

Flex Catering has the most advanced online ordering for food businesses including features such as cut-off times, minimum order quantity, multiple delivery times, order notes and more.
Kitchen Production Tools:

Flex Catering has comprehensive tools and reports to assist in the kitchen. Advanced reports, interface for kitchen tablet, costing, prep-sheet and delivery calendar are among the tools available.
Advanced Product Management:

Flex Catering has the flexibility that caterers, restaurants and cafes need for their products, allowing the configuration of different types of products such as combo and pack, dietary requirements and more.

name: Workshop Software
tag_line: Complete management for Auto Shop plus integrations to major Automotive Systems
details:
Workshop Software is a very simple to use, yet effective, Workshop Management System for any business that does Service and repairs.

From Bookings, through to Job management, invoices, quotes and much more, Workshop Software handles all the day-to-day management of running a Workshop. 

Ensure customers come back to your Workshop with our unique, automated service reminder system that lets you set-and-forget. Simply turn on automatic reminders for a steady stream of customers coming back into your business for more work.

With many automotive integrations, including CarFax and PartTech, along with Vehicle Visuals, you'll be supercharged.

Workshop Software integrates directly with QuickBooks. Take out the simple process of setting up the integration, including mapping of some accounts, then you're up and running. 

Workshop Software has a two-way sync with QuickBooks including Customers, Suppliers, Sales Invoices, Purchase Invoices, payments and receipts, all in real time.

Let Workshop Software handle your front-end workflow management for your Workshop, while QuickBooks handles all the back-end.

Free, no-obligation trial.
key_benefits:
Want to take out the hassles of running your Workshop? 

Workshop Software can be set-up in a matter of minutes, is super easy to use and carries out all the day-to-day functions of running your workshop.
Seamless integration with QuickBooks means that you can carry out the day-to-day running of your shop, while QuickBooks, you Bookkeeper and Accountant take care of the back end. 

Real-time integration ensures QuickBooks and Workshop are in sync.
Workshop Software is dedicated to on-going updates and features to ensure your business is ahead of your competition. With a proven track record of delivering exciting updates, usually at no extra cost to you.

name: Glances
tag_line: Glance at all your data, everywhere.
details:
Glance at all your data, everywhere. Eliminate tab switching, searching & clicking around to find important information. Glances finds data based on what you are looking at. This no-code solution brings everything you need into one handy-to-use spot.

We can support any application that provides an industry standard API, including custom applications. Here are some of the applications that we support: QuickBooks, Salesforce, Shopify, Zendesk, Stripe, Mailchimp, JIRA, SugarCRM, Zoho, Constant Contact, SuiteCRM, Groove, and many more.

Have other applications that you use? Just let us know and we will work to add support for those as well.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Glances enables you to see related data based on what you are currently looking at by pulling information in real time from across your various workplace platforms and apps. When an email address appears on the page, you simply click the browser extension to see data from QuickBooks or any other application you use. That works just the same when you are using QuickBooks. Glances shows you related data from your other applications while you view your data in QuickBooks.
key_benefits:
Eliminate tab switching and stay focused on whatever you are working on. Need to know something important about what you are working on, but it is in another system? Use Glances to view it right now to avoid painful app switching.
See what matters to you right here, right now. Whether working on a support case, a new lead, or anything else, glance at any emails, invoices, notes, etc residing in some other app when you need it, right now.
Only takes minutes to set up while also reducing your license costs. Not every user in your company needs to log into each and every one of your applications. Save on licensing costs by giving them just the insights they need with Glances.

[{'question': "What is different about JuvodHR's Job Descriptions?", 'answer': "Our Job Descriptions have already been written for you by top industry experts. Plus, you can easily edit them to match your organization's needs. 

We are the only system that allows you to access our extensive database of occupations and edit the results of your search. We have customized the information available on O*NET, the nation's primary source of occupational information, developed under the sponsorship of the US Department of Labor."}, {'question': 'What is the best way to use the JuvodHR Scores?', 'answer': 'The JuvodHR Score provides management a fair and valid way to stack rank employees. The JuvodHR Score is valid across all the jobs in your organization, regardless of salary. 

You may consider stack ranking employees with the same job title and/or stack ranking employees by department.

You may also want to stack rank all of the employees in your organization to give you a clear picture of good performers vs. not so good performers. This will also help you decide how to distribute bonuses.'}, {'question': "How is an employee's JuvodHR Score determined?", 'answer': "Our experts have developed a statistically valid weighted system that calculates an employee's JuvodHR Score based on his or her performance ratings.

All Tasks and Work Styles are first rated on a scale of 1 to 7:

1.0 to 3.9 = Needs Improvement,
4.0 to 6.0 = Meets Expectations,
6.1 to 7.0 = Exceeds Expectations.

We weight each of these ratings based upon the item's importance to the job as determined by list order, then average those weighted ratings to calculate the JuvodHR Score."}, {'question': 'Where did the Tasks and Work Styles in your Job Descriptions and Performance Reviews come from?', 'answer': 'The top Tasks and Work Styles for each job presented in JuvodHR?s Job Descriptions and Performance Reviews are based on research from O*NET?s data collection program. JuvodHR has drawn the top 10 Tasks and the top 8 Work Styles from O*NET?s database. The data, collected from three sources ? workers, occupation experts, and occupation analysts ? is used to provide complete information for each occupation.

Experts at JuvodHR have customized some of the tasks for you, to make them more meaningful'}]

name: Lightyear
tag_line: Purchasing & AP Automation - Data-Extraction | Automated Bookkeeping | Approvals
details:
Lightyear is a Purchasing and Accounts Payable Platform that saves your teams up to 80% of their time. We have two optional product modules; Purchasing & Accounts Payables. 
Purchasing - Import your POs from QuickBooks or create them in Lightyear. Prevent fraud across with our approvals matrix. Receive goods against POs and allow Lightyear to do the heavy lifting with our Automated 3-Way line-by-line Matching.
Accounts Payable - Suppliers email their standard bills, credit notes and statements, which have line-item data extracted in real-time. Bills are then presented to individual managers at the start of a customisable approvals workflow.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Lightyear is integrated with QuickBooks Online for the seamless transfer of financial data between the 2 systems. All relevant data is extracted from your bills in Lightyear, categorised and exported into QuickBooks Online, ready for payment by your accountant. We send suppliers (vendors), GL categories, items, chart of accounts, tax rates, bills and credit notes, into QuickBooks. Lightyear can import your POs created in QuickBooks to allow you to complete Automated 3-Way Matching.
key_benefits:
Immediate and accurate line-item data-extraction: Lightyear extracts line-item data from bills, credit notes, supplier statements, receipts and purchase orders immediately and accurately, in real time. Lightyear applies rules line by line.
Approvals process - Customisable approval workflow. Real time routing of bills and orders to the correct approvers. You can dispute and communicate on each bill using the notes feature, before exporting to QuickBooks Online.
Leverage the latest technology to automate and streamline your purchasing processes. Import your Purchase Orders (POs) from QuickBooks, receive goods against POs and let Lightyear do the heavy lifting with our Automated 3-Way line-by-line matching.

?paskr Owner = QuickBooks Customer
?paskr Job = QuickBooks Job

name: GoBenefits ~ Group Benefits - Made Easy

details:
Small businesses can quickly view rates of multiple medical, dental, vision plan, life & STD/LTD plans.

Choosing a health care plan for your small business would be easy if your employees were all the same. But, they?re not. You?ve got younger and older adults, some are single, some have families and some may be managing chronic health conditions. Each person might have a different health concern or preference when selecting health care benefits. If you have more than 5 employees, our system can send health underwriting applications for level funded and Association Health Plans.  If you are an ALE (applicable large employer), GoBenefits synch's your time data to determine eligibility based on monthly for ACA lookback criteria as well as 1095 reporting.
key_benefits:
Free instant group quoting of UHC medical, dental, vision, life, & STD/LTD.  Level-Funded plans for 5-99 and ACR for 2-50 - No paperwork!!  

GoBenefits is a national insurance agency exclusively for small businesses.
Benefits Enrollment - Enroll the entire company electronically.  Employees simply add their selected plans into a shopping cart.  

Dedicated phone support is also available for employees needing enrollment assistance.
Ongoing Administration - Manage new hires, terms and life events easily.  All eligibility changes are communicated directly to the carrier.

name: Uncat
tag_line: Fix uncategorized transactions with client notes and sync to QuickBooks Online.
details:
Uncat looks for uncategorized transactions in QuickBooks Online and notifies your clients. 

Your clients add notes and receipts via Uncat and everything syncs with QuickBooks Online. 

Uncat notifies you that uncategorized expenses are ready to be assigned to accounts. 

You choose the right accounts and Uncat syncs your selections with QuickBooks Online.

More features:

* Assign client users to specific payment accounts. (e.g. Assign Lisa to the AmEx card.)

* Style Uncat with your company logo and brand color.

* Post questions and instructions for your client.

* Categorize expenses across all of your clients from one screen in Uncat.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
1. Start a free trial and connect QuickBooks Online.

2. Invite your clients to join Uncat. 

3. Your clients add notes and receipts to uncategorized transactions.

4. You assign transactions to accounts. Uncat syncs to QuickBooks Online.
key_benefits:
We?ll notify your clients by email (and SMS) if they have uncategorized expenses, uncategorized income, or uncategorized assets so that they can add notes and receipts online via Uncat.

You don't have to export spreadsheets of transactions anymore.
Uncat automatically syncs client notes and receipts for uncategorized transactions to QuickBooks Online. 

You can assign expenses to accounts via Uncat or in QuickBooks Online.

You don?t have to copy-paste client notes or manually upload receipts.
Start a 14-day free trial.
pricing_text: Start a 14-day free trial. $5/client/month after the trial.

name: Shopventory
tag_line: Advanced multi-channel inventory and reporting for your business.
details:
Shopventory provides an inventory management platform that seamlessly works with Point-of-Sale as well as e-commerce solutions to help your business perform at its best. 

Shopventory keeps track of all of your sales to keep your multi-channel inventory up to date. This sales information along with your inventory values and profitability can be synced to your QuickBooks Online account to make it easier to keep your books accurate. 

Easily choose the pieces of information that you want synced to QuickBooks Online.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Shopventory works with QuickBooks Online by syncing your sales information and inventory values to make it easier for you or your accountant to keep your books up to date.

Details that are synced include but not limited to:

1. Payments by payment type
2. Sales tax collected
3. Fees paid for credit card processing (may be unavailable depending on your processor)
4. Inventory values by category
key_benefits: Sync your sales and inventory values to QuickBooks Online from any integration that works with Shopventory. Shopventory works with Square, Clover, PayPal Here, and Shopify with many more coming soon.

The system pulls in invoices, payment history, credit memos, and contact email addresses on an automatic schedule, or simply on demand.

Payments made in the portal (even partials) automatically record and apply to the invoices in QuickBooks eliminating manual entry.

Pay based on $ amount, QuickBooks Terms or even a CRM/PSA contract!
Professional looking Client Portal that fits your brand. Customers have complete billing transparency and management. They are able to view, print & pay new or historic invoices 24/7 via credit card or low cost Electronic Check (ACH).

name: Telephone Timesheets
tag_line: Track employee time from any phone.  $3 per user.
details:
Telephone Timesheets allows you to track employee time and location using any telephone.  

Telephone Timesheets is the only app-less, self-learning, time tracking solution on the market. That means no setup for you, and no training for your employees. If they can place a phone call, and respond to a text message, they are ready. Your employees start calling immediately. When they do, we will automatically add them to the system and check them in and out, and you will get automatic reports on hours worked per employee and per job. 

It is ideal for field-based employees who need to check in and check out through a land line or mobile phone.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Telephone Timesheets allows you to import employee data, customer data, and service item data from QuickBooks Online.  It also allows you to export timesheet entries directly to QuickBooks Online for payroll processing.
