name: Flowrev
tag_line: Automate cost & deferred revenue recognition. Be Accurate, Compliant, Efficient.
details: Flowrev is online cost and revenue recognition software that lets users automate and streamline their accounting processes for deferred revenue and prepaid expenses. By eliminating time consuming spreadsheets users close faster and regularly deliver more accurate financials and forecasts.  New regulations (IFRS15, ASC606) for revenue and expense recognition go into effect for private companies worldwide in 2018. Now's the time to implement revenue and expense recognition automation software. Beyond regulations, the more accurate financials, which are reflective of true business operations, are a must have for company executives.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Flowrev is seamlessly integrated with QuickBooks Online.  Users can easily pull transaction data incrementally to Flowrev, automatically generate revenue and cost recognition schedules and journal back to QuickBooks with the click of a button. Changes to transactions in QuickBooks are easy to keep track of and handle with the built-in schedule checkers, which highlight transaction changes that require follow on revrec/costrec processing. Product and service bundles are fully supported, as are multiple deferred revenue and recognition accounts.
key_benefits:
Streamline your cost and revenue recognition accounting processes by eliminating hard to maintain spreadsheets and tedious hand entered journals. Close faster with more accurate financials. Easily deliver relevant schedule based forecasts & metrics.
Quickly generate and journal flexible, GAAP/IFRS compliant, per line schedules based upon powerful recognition parameters and exact service dates. Easily handle changes with full trackability. Run built-in checks to prevent revenue, expense leakage.
Instantly view waterfall reports and schedule based forecasts to assess future revenue and expenses. Leverage automatically updated business metrics such as MRR, ARR to better manage your business. Easily access and review contracts starts and ends.
pricing_text: Flowrev subscriptions deliver high value at low cost. Try for free for 14-days, avail a discount by pre-paying annually. Accountants - check out the volume plans. Details at: https://flowrev.com/pricing

name: Bitcoin Sync by Blockpath
tag_line: Sync Bitcoin Transactions + Capital Gains Reports into QuickBooks
details:
Blockpath syncs Bitcoin transactions into QuickBooks to make your accounting simpler. Provide us your Bitcoin addresses or xPubs, sort them into groups, and then relax. 

We will create all your transactions inside QuickBooks, along with records of your ongoing capital gains obligations. The app automatically recognizes payments from clients/mining, exchange sale conversions, and transfers between your addresses.

You don't have to worry if the data is correct, we provide reconcile tools that show you every transaction on the blockchain and within QuickBooks, and can automatically repair any discrepancies quickly.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: We create accounts in your Chart of Accounts for each Bitcoin address/xPub. Transactions are automatically created in the account when they occur, with the exchange rate attached. For outgoing transactions, the app also records the capital gain/loss in an income account. You can manually set the QuickBooks customer, memo, tax code, and transaction type, or you can create a rule to automatically set them.
key_benefits:
Bring together your Bitcoin accounting and traditional accounting to make tracking your finances easier. Monitor your balances, transactions, and ongoing capital gains earnings from directly inside your QuickBooks account.
You'll get your Bitcoin transactions sorted directly into your QuickBooks Online every hour, complete with your notes and the exchange rate at the time of transaction for tax purposes.

name: DAVO Sales Tax
tag_line: Fully Automate Sales Tax - Sets Aside Daily and Pays on Time and in Full for You
details: For 39.99 a month DAVO Sales Tax will collect, file, and pay your sales tax. First month is free. No long-term contracts, no boarding fee, and no cancellation fee.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: During sign up, DAVO Sales Tax will ask for permission to read your sales and tax data through your POS. After sign up, DAVO Sales Tax will periodically access your QuickBooks invoices (several times each day) to determine the daily net sales tax collected and sales and returns data at each configured tax rate. DAVO then impounds the net sales tax on a daily basis via ACH to your bank account. As appropriate for your situation, DAVO will file your sales tax return with your state and pay the sales tax due to your State from the funds impounded daily.
key_benefits:
Stress-free, hassle-free sales tax. From the second your POS enters a sale to the moment your state receives your tax payment, you won?t have to do a thing. Once installed, DAVO runs in the background and doesn?t need to be touched.
No extra work. No shuffling money around. No missed or late payments. No guessing if you have enough to cover the tax bill. No paperwork. No checks. And most importantly, no more worrying about sales tax ever again.
DAVO is less expensive than an accountant and less time-consuming than trying to navigate tax compliance yourself. Plus, it has tons of user-friendly features to help keep your finances in order.
pricing_text: For 39.99 a month DAVO sets aside your sales tax daily, pays your taxes on-time and in full, sends daily sales and tax report emails, and has live phone, chat and email support. First month is free.

name: OwnerRez
tag_line: A vacation rental booking engine, built by people who own vacation rentals
details: When bookings are created or updated in your OwnerRez account, our system will create corresponding updates in your QuickBooks account. Each OwnerRez booking is mapped to a single "invoice" in QuickBooks and payments are synced as well.  An OwnerRez "booking" is the same as a QuickBooks "invoice".  OwnerRez determines if an invoice exists in QuickBooks for the booking in question.  If not, it creates a new invoice. If it exists, it updates the current invoice. Read more about OwnerRez and QuickBooks here
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Once QuickBooks is connected and configured for a property, all bookings that are changed thereafter will start syncing with QuickBooks. OwnerRez will silently send data to your QuickBooks account, under the covers, without you doing anything or pressing any buttons.  Bookings and payments from OwnerRez are turned into Invoices and Received Payments in QuickBooks. Sign up for OwnerRez now or click here to Connect your existing OwnerRez account
key_benefits:
Record your OwnerRez bookings and payment into QuickBooks without lifting a finger. When bookings and payments change, the matching records in QuickBooks also change.
Map rent and surcharge amounts to different classes, locations an departments based on your different vacation rental properties.
Map vacation rental payments to different bank accounts in QuickBooks based on the type of payment (check, cash, credit card, PayPal)

name: Stripe Sync by Acodei
tag_line: Sync your Stripe transactions with QuickBooks Online - affordable and easy!
details: Our app is built for anyone, from business owners to accountants. Use our step-by-step onboarding to set up everything you need. Connect your Stripe and QuickBooks Online accounts for easy, automated syncing. Instead of just seeing a lump Stripe Transfer in your account, you will see each transaction broken down with customer information, date of sale, Stripe fees, and description. This is particularly useful if you are trying to track customer data or daily transaction data in QuickBooks. Customize the data flow how you like to see it in QuickBooks, and don't waste your time with manual accounting processes.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: When you first connect your QuickBooks Online account, you will be led to our step-by-step onboarding process. There you can connect your Stripe account and set up all of the mapping for products and accounts. After completing the onboarding process, we will automatically sync your transactions as they come in from Stripe. You simply need to continue to monitor your bank statements, matching deposits as they come through.
key_benefits:
Sales and Refund Syncing: As you receive transactions through Stripe, our app syncs your transactions by creating Sales and Refund Receipts in QuickBooks in real time. These receipts will contain transaction details from Stripe, including fees.
Payout Syncing: As you receive payouts/withdrawals, our app creates a Bank Deposit or Expense for you that pre-selects your Sales and Refund Receipts. You get a matched deposit for every Stripe payout.
Historical Transactions: Sync previous months worth of data seamlessly, and view your data feed to make sure all data has properly synced. Historical syncing is available for $10 per historic month.
pricing_text:
Free trial up to 30 transactions per month, no credit card required.
Monthly plans - $9 a month for up to 1,000 transactions, $19 a month up to 10,000.
Historic syncing is $10 per historic month for up to 1,000 transactions a month.

name: Shogo
tag_line: Seamless integration from your Point Of Sale to QuickBooks
details:
Shogo has partnered with most of the leading edge Point of Sale Providers available:

- Micros
- ShopKeep 
- NCR Silver
- Lavu
- Lightspeed 
- Square
- Cake
- Upserve
- Rezku
- Toast
- TouchBistro
- Touchpoint
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Keep your daily sales from your POS and QuickBooks Online in sync in 3 easy steps:

1). CONNECT: Create a Shogo account and connect your Point of Sale or E-Commerce system to your accounting system. You will soon be on your way to automated, daily entries.

2). MAP: Map your Point of Sale data to your accounting system. Including Revenues, Revenue Offsets, Taxes, Tenders, and Cash Drawer events.

3). POST: Once your Shogo configuration is activated, Shogo will begin posting automatic entries every morning.
key_benefits: Shogo is a cloud-based service that seamlessly books your sales data directly from your Point of Sale system to QuickBooks automatically, every day with no manual intervention or data entry required.

details:

No more manual data entry or uploading CSVs, with Bnbtally you can eliminate human error and save countless hours each month in accounting. Each Airbnb reservation can be automatically synced and allocated in detail based on the accounting codes and tracking categories you set. 

Bnbtally is a registered trademark of Tally Lytics LLC.

Easily allocate revenue, taxes, Airbnb service fees, cleaning fees, commissions, trust accounts and more!

name: clickBACON
tag_line: The fastest and easiest way to control your food, beverage and labor cost
details:
BACON is the simplest software available for restaurant owners & operators to keep their food, beverage, and labor costs under control in real-time. 
    
Forget confusing POS Data and Spreadsheet Hell that just keeps you guessing!  Instead, you'll have accurate and actionable data that gives you insights you CAN use to increase profits.
   
Designed by restaurant operators for restaurant operators, BACON helps remove the stress of keeping track of restaurant financials. BACON tracks everything you need so you can stop guessing your way to a more profitable restaurant.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: Connect your QuickBooks account to BACON to easily track food, beverage and labor cost.  We will automatically pull in your sales, purchases, and labor which means you can avoid double entering all of your information.
key_benefits:

details: Click to start using a Free Trial of AutoEntry
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
AutoEntry integrates seamlessly with QuickBooks and extracts the required data before posting it into your QuickBooks account. AutoEntry is also a smart solution and remembers how you categorize expenses so you won't ever have to categorize them again


Here?s how you get started

 - Scan, snap or email a copy of the document you want to capture
 - AutoEntry extracts and analyzes your data
 - Once done, items will appear in your inbox for you to approve into QuickBooks
 - If you prefer, AutoEntry will auto-publish known vendors saving even more time
key_benefits:
No more manual data entry: For bills, receipts, sales invoices, bank and card statements and more, AutoEntry automates data entry. Simply scan, take a photo with our mobile app, or send your documents via email and AutoEntry will do the rest
Go paperless: Once AutoEntry has captured and entered your data, it creates a digital record of the image and attaches it to the transaction in QuickBooks. You?ll no longer need to store paper copies, so your office can declutter and go green
Grow your business: If you're a plumber, be a plumber - not a bookkeeper. If you own a coffee shop, make coffee. AutoEntry empowers small business owners, allowing them to focus more time on running their business, and less on the paperwork
pricing_text: AutoEntry pricing is based on a credit system.  To scan a bill, invoice or receipt will use up one credit, a purchase invoice with line items will use two credits and a bank statement will use three credits.

name: PrintBoss Online
tag_line: Simple check printing - multiple bank accounts, one check stock.
details: PrintBoss Online prints checks from QuickBooks Online. The magic is that PrintBoss Online also determines the name of the company and the bank account for each check. As a result, you print all of your checks onto blank check stock and the correct company and bank information is printed on every check. This means you have only one check stock for all companies and bank accounts. Or don't store any check stock and let us print and mail your checks with the PrintBoss Check Printing Service. This way you can process checks from any device, anywhere, with no need of a printer or stock. PrintBoss Online saves you money and increases security.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Enter check payments as you normally enter them in QuickBooks Online. 

Login to PrintBoss Online and execute 3 steps:

1)	IMPORT: When you want to print checks, open the PrintBoss Online app and click ?Import?.

2)	GENERATE: Select individual checks or all imported checks and click on ?Generate?.

3)	PRINT: When you click on ?Print?, all checks that have been generated will be printed to the printer that you select. You can select checks individually if you do not want to print all generated checks.

PrintBoss communicates back to QuickBooks so all checks printed by PrintBoss show in QB.
key_benefits:
Print checks from multiple bank accounts onto one check stock. This means lower costs and increased security. Blank check stock (stock with nothing preprinted on its face) costs a fraction of what preprinted checks cost, and unused stock is secure.
Enable the PrintBoss Check Printing Service and Wellspring Software will print and mail your checks for you. By removing the labor and supply costs of check printing, you save time and money, while maintaining control of your AP processes.
Approve and sign checks with a tap of a button on your device. Email alerts inform users that checks require their attention. PrintBoss Online is designed to increase efficiency and lower accounts payable processing time.

name: Rewind Backups
tag_line: Automatic Backups, Restores, and Copy for QuickBooks Online
details:
Protect hours of work by automatically backing up or copying your QuickBooks Online files. Enjoy the freedom to undo individual changes or restore your entire file if needed. Never deal with another manual backup again. 
 From the team behind the top-rated backup app for Shopify and BigCommerce, you can now take control of your accounting data.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Connections to the QuickBooks Online API are always made securely and your most important data is stored encrypted in our secure Rewind Vault?. 
 Link one or all the QuickBooks Online company files you manage to begin your first full Rewind backup. All future changes in your QuickBooks Online files are automatically backed up within five minutes. You have access to all your backups inside the secure Rewind Vault.
key_benefits:
Always Up To Date   Unfortunately, mistakes and data disasters happen. Enjoy peace of mind knowing that changes to your company files are automatically backed up every time you use QuickBooks Online.
Flexible Data Restore  Get complete flexibility over how you restore your data: quickly rewind a single item, multiple items or your entire company file to a previous point in time. Ensure that your other work is not lost when you restore.
Save Hours Of Time  Tasks that took hours of manual setup like onboarding new clients to your QuickBooks Online Accountant plans, configuring new accounts, or testing third-party apps can be done in the click of a button with Rewind Copy.

[{'question': 'If QuickBooks Online is in the cloud, why do I need a backup?', 'answer': "Cloud services like QuickBooks Online are backed up to be able to recover the entire platform after a disaster - like if a hurricane compromised their servers. This is a disaster recovery backup and is not accessible to you or Intuit's support team if something goes wrong in your individual file. That's why Rewind automatically backs up your company files within minutes of any changes and gives you access to restore them when you need to."}, {'question': 'How do I restore a QuickBooks Online backup with Rewind?', 'answer': 'You can restore a single item or the entire file back to a previous time/state, like an undo button. With Rewind Copy now available, you can also restore your backup to another QuickBooks Online file.'}, {'question': 'What does Rewind for QuickBooks Online backup?', 'answer': 'TRANSACTIONS: Bills, Bill Payments, Credit Memos, Deposits, Estimates, Invoices, Journal Entries, Payments, Purchases, Purchase Orders, Refund Receipts, Sales Receipts, Time Activities, Transfers, Vendors.

 LISTS: Accounts, Classes, Customers, Departments, Employees (except SSN field), Items, Journal Codes (France only), Payment Methods, Terms, Vendors.

 OTHER: Attachments, Budgets, Currencies, Tax Agencies, Tax Codes, Tax Rates, Preferences.'}, {'question': 'What does Rewind for QuickBooks Online NOT backup?', 'answer': "At this time, Rewind for QuickBooks Online does not backup or restore the following items: Company Info, Entitlements, Exchange Rates, QuickBooks Online Payments API, and Payroll.

 The QuickBooks Online API does not grant permissions to app developers to access this data. Since we don't have access to it, performing a restore on your file will not affect any of this data. We are actively working with Intuit to improve Rewind's functionality for you."}]

name: Hala.ai
tag_line: Intelligent Assistant. Tailored for QuickBooks Online.
details:
Hala leverages AI technologies to simplify and streamline the processes and tasks connected to QuickBooks. Hala takes responsibility for daily routine activities, allowing users to have more time for value-adding work.
The Hala intelligent assistant uses voice, text queries, and a natural-language user interface to answer questions, visualize data, and perform actions while being integrated to QuickBooks. Hala adapts to every user's language expressions, queries, and preferences through time.  
Hala supports a wide range of user queries (Digital Skills) and continuously learns new Digital Skills to help you during more processes and tasks.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Hala works like a digital assistant for the users of QuickBooks Online, the same as "Siri" works with Apple devices. Hala has different features integrated, known as Digital Skills. The purpose of them is to help you be more productive. For example, "Give me a sales report" is one Digital Skill, "Create a new bill" is another one. With Hala, you spend less time keeping books accurate and up to date.
When you talk to Hala, Hala sends the API request to QuickBooks Online, processes the response, and displays the answer in the chat.
key_benefits:
Hala can create transactional data faster than you can. Hala can perform monotonous activities in a faster, easier, and more intelligent way. Let her create a purchase order, add time activity, create invoices or expenses in a blink of an eye.
Hala knows about your business. Quickly check facts about your customers or vendors. Get quick data about your bank, financial ratios, employees, and other master and transactional data. It?s as simple as asking.
Hala is a faster, easier way to get all kinds of useful reports. Get sales reports by products, customers, periods, locations. Get profit and loss, balance sheet, and compare them with previous periods, and many more.

name: kopilot
tag_line: Put a CFO in your back pocket!
details:
Call it business intelligence, performance management, reporting, or analytics. kopilot's goal remains the same: providing you accurate and updated knowledge.  Make sure your business is running well, while you can focus on what imports the most to you.

Thank kopilot, you can:
* predict your sales at the end of the (fiscal) year;
* monitor your transactions in real-time, without moving a finger;
* save time in the invoices' follow up. 
* better manage your retainers.

Having updated vital business information has never been easier!
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
1. Create your account on kopilot.io.
2. It will request you to grant access to your QuickBooks Online account.
3. Once you accepted, kopilot syncs all your data. That operation can take up to 3 minutes. Your data is transformed, is enriched for information of quality- and useful.
4. Afterward, QuickBooks Online notifies kopilot (and pushes the information to kopilot) each time something changed within your QuickBooks account.
5. Every night, kopilot operates a control check by requesting full sync of your data.
6. When edgy for the next sync, you always can request immediate sync.
key_benefits:
Put a CFO in your back pocket?leverage on your accounting data to get the analytical job done. Focus on your core business: making money. Meanwhile, kopilot monitors your operations, analyzes your data, writes insights, and suggests actions.
Five minutes a day! That's all it takes to make sure your business is running well or to get the actions to take back the control of your operations. Control your company anywhere, anytime, and in real-time. kopilot works perfectly on your devices.
Be guided when lost. It is not just about managing your business with KPIs. kopilot goes beyond by writing insights, by providing action plans, by suggesting actions or proposing articles to read for one purpose: helping you never to be stuck.
pricing_text: It's a no brainer. The pricing is an all-inclusive monthly subscription to benefit limitless from kopilot: unlimited users, unlimited data, all features. kopilot comes with a 14-day free trial. Afterward, pay only if you love it.

name: CPA Alerts
tag_line: Instantly turn transactions into a management dashboard and daily text alerts
details: CPAAlerts seamlessly connects to QuickBooks Online to unlock powerful, actionable insights for your business. Easily access a dashboard of your organization?s key activity trends to make timely, well-informed business decisions every day. With VitalSign Alerts, key managers stay connected to your business activity through text and email alerts generated whenever entries are entered into your QuickBooks Online account.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
CPAAlerts leverages the QuickBooks Online authentication protocol to connect to your account. It also uses the QuickBooks Online API to pull account data to analyze and provide visualizations. We secure your data using industry standard and QuickBooks Online API compliant data practices. (HTTPS, Encrypted Tokens, Secure Cookies and more) 

Once connected, CPAAlerts analyzes Quickbooks Online entries each day to update visualizations and to generate automated text and email alerts that are sent to the recipients you choose.
key_benefits:
See your QuickBooks Online entries transformed into a powerful dashboard with charts of sales orders, bank balances, receivables and payables aging, expenditures, and deposits.
Send automatically generated text and email alerts to key managers whenever QuickBooks Online entries are made that are important to them or their department.
Keep key members of your team armed and ready to take action with better, more timely information every day.
pricing_text: CPAAlerts offers three, flexible pricing plans to meet the needs of QuickBooks Online users.

name: Businest
tag_line: Learn HOW to Boost Your Cash Flow in Under 8 Minutes
details:
Step-by-step business coaching, video training, & expert tips (across sales, marketing, finance, leadership and operations) to help you make more money doing what you love.
Grow profitably & future proof your business. Businest? (business coaching) is so much more than just dashboards, cash flow forecasts and KPIs - we show you HOW to fix problems and prevent them from recurring.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Once you authorize your connection to QBO, we upload your complete financial history, calculate your cash flow position, create a 12 month forecast (including Profit & Loss, Balance Sheet and Cash Flow Statement), set up What if Analysis, & deliver step-by-step business coaching tips in under 8 minutes. 
We do all the heavy lifting - our proprietary a.i. algorithm combs through hundreds of KPIs and scenarios to determine which 2-3 things you must do this month to boost profitability, cash flow, & grow your business profitably and safely.
key_benefits:
Businest? uses a.i. to sort through your numbers & determine which actions will have the biggest impact on bottom line & cash flow.  We deliver step-by-step business coaching to show you HOW to fix problems & prevent recurrences.
Dashboards, graphs , & forecasts only confirm you have a cash flow problem.  Businest? shows you how to FIX it. Replace guesswork, & sleepless nights with peace of mind - HOW to grow safely & put more money in your bank account.
Avoid nasty surprises. See the impact of every decision before you make it. Ask better questions, make better decisions & get better results. Get expert tips across sales, marketing, financials, & leadership aspects of your business.

name: Manufacturing Operations & Inventory Management
tag_line: Better Business Decisions with Connected Data.
details: DataNinja helps you run Inventory and Manufacturing operations with control, visibility, and traceability. Affordably automate away error-prone, manual data entry. Stop using spreadsheets to stay ahead of inventory operations.
how_it_works_with_quick_books:
Customer Transactions
-Estimates, Invoices, Sales Receipts
-Customers, Order Lifecycle
-Packing lists, Memos, Links, Notes
-Tracking Information
-Custom Reports

Vendor Transactions
-Purchase Orders, Bills, Checks, Expenses
-Custom Fields
-Reorder Point/Quantity
-Vendor Details
-Memos, Links, Notes

Inventory and Manufacturing Operations:
-Inventor Items
-Inventory Valuation
-Unit of Measure
-Adjustments
-Cycle Counts
-Manufacturing Expense
-Custom Fields, Classes, Categories, Divisions
-Direct Labor and Overhead Costs.
key_benefits:
Stop wasting time and money bouncing between part-outs and over buying. The MRP algorithm accounts for vendor lead time and inventory supply/demand through multi-level bills of material. Traceability powers the cost and margin feed to QuickBooks.
If you can make traceability and quality control easy, it gets done. Add real-time data verification to each inventory transaction so errors are caught in-the-moment. Connects the financial impacts of quality and operations activities to Quickbooks.
Receiving and shipping transactions update QuickBooks product quantity in real-time. Within DataNinja, unique inventory identifiers group quantities by location. Barcoded bin locations make it easy to perform cycle counts and transfers.

name: TRXio
tag_line: TRXio is a cloud-based inventory management system with item-level traceability
details: TRXio? offers simple-to-use desktop and mobile apps for order fulfillment and project organization to increase estimate-to-invoice accuracy. The system eliminates labor-intensive and error-prone physical inventory counts done with manual or double-entry inventory control by utilizing cell phones or tablets to scan items at any point of the delivery route for live, real-time geographic coordinates. This allows field techs to scan inventory on location and create change orders on the fly. Customizable LiveQR codes ease the reordering process and provide easy access to product usage and warranty information.
how_it_works_with_quick_books: TRXio? integrates with QuickBooks to synchronize customer, vendor and product information to help organize valuable resources and assets, increase profitability, and minimize costs. The system pulls estimates from QuickBooks to create orders in TRXio? for fulfillment, pushes closed/completed orders from TRXio? back to QuickBooks as invoices, creates item receipts in QuickBooks to complete the purchasing loop for received items and generates separate reports from QuickBooks. TRXio? secures data by limiting access to restricted personnel who don't need access to accounting or reporting.
key_benefits:
TRXio? is a cloud-based inventory management solution that integrates with QuickBooks Online to effectively manage assets and inventory through real-time product traceability, movement analytics and robust inventory reporting.
TRXio? includes features such as order management, project organization, standardized identification, labeling, cycle counts, auditing, change orders, vendor PO's, and LiveQR codes linked to fully customizable free post-sale marketing web pages.
By increasing inventory consistency and collecting more accurate data, TRXio? provides fast and easy access to reports to help your company uncover hidden profits and build accountability. We call this Inventory Enlightenment?.

Data for your stores is gathered across locations, allowing you to organize your stores.

After setting up your GL accounts in QuickBooks Online with your bookkeeper, you map these accounts to fields in Lightspeed Accounting for payment methods, cost of goods sold, revenue, and so on.

If ever there is a discrepancy, a dashboard makes it easy to compare data between QuickBooks and Lightspeed.
